data.description: The perfect opportunity to own a beautiful, well maintained move in ready home on a corner lot in in Fairway Crossing, conveniently located near shopping, dining, entertainment, and schools. The home features a split bedroom floor plan with a private bath and walk-in closet in the master suite, a large living area with vaulted ceilings, eat in kitchen with granite countertops, covered front porch, large patio, and a full privacy fence. A nearby neighborhood park provides a great space for outdoor activities. The roof was replaced in 2020 and the HVAC system was replaced in 2022.
